biography: Rosa works as a Data Scientist at the German Federal Ministry for Family Affairs, Senior Citizens, Women and Youth, where she is currently supporting the setup of an in-house Data Lab. As an interdisciplinary thinker with experience in national and EU policymaking, she is interested in sustainable solutions at the intersection of policy, psychology, and data science.
